list.name: Default
list.comment:
Added multithreading, scheduled events, property management gui,logging, security, and improved architecture
Multithreading allows the user to have a better experience and allows a set number of events in a queue. Scheduling allows inventory levels to be updated using cron syntax. Began a gui to allow users to modify properties of the application. Followed security best practices. Refactored project to be more modular and maintainable through the use of design patterns.
